headline: Innovative Algorithm Slashes Time to Solve Massive Optimization Problems
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., January 27, 2025--FICO (NYSE: FICO): Global analytics software leader FICO today announced that the 2024 FICO® Xpress Best Paper Award went to a team that developed an algorithm for finding solutions to difficult optimization problems with millions of variables and constraints in just a few seconds.
